text: Jetty Paerl (Henriette Nanette Paerl; 27 May 1921 â€“ 22 August 2013) was a Dutch singer. She was most famous in the 1950s and 1960s. Paerl was born on 27 May 1921 in Amsterdam, Netherlands. She was married to Dutch artist Cees Bantzinger.
